This is the XHIBIT Display localproxy.

It is called by the CDU, giving the MAC Address of the CDU.

I uses the Mac Address to lookup from local proxy database the attributes
of the CDU, including the URL of the page to display.

It uses the URL to fetch the content and then uses a local python script to
transform the HTML fetched to XML, and finally, enriches the XML with data
from the local proxy database to be used by the CDU (e.g. the CDU title and
location).
